      "text": "Zoku: The Legend of Bishin (美神伝説Ｚｏｋｕ, Bishin Densetsu Zoku) is a hybrid racing and beat 'em up video game that was developed and published by Magifact for the Super Famicom in 1993 only in Japan.",
